insert into events values(2134567,10000,'2016/04/01','34 Mason St','SF','CA','94102','images/content/food1.png','BEER','Brewery touring and beverage sampling Beer Socials Private tastings Beer festivals And much more','The San Francisco Bay Area is host to many of the best and most unique beer producers in the country. Some are considered mirco-breweries, only producing enough fermented beverage for their customers, while others produce for an international audience.Beer Socials is dedicated to a wide variety of beer tasting activities including; Brewery touring and beverage sampling Beer Socials Private tastings Beer festivals And much more','food','MyTreat','#beer');
insert into events values(2134577,10001,'2016/04/02','302 6th Ave','SF','CA','94118','images/content/food2.png','Whiskey','An evening of Scotch and Whiskey drinking usually goes hand in hand with good conversation in relaxed company. I look forward to a comfortable and vibrant group.','Scotch and Whiskey drinkers of the Bay Area Unite! If you are a connoisseur of Scotch and Whiskey Ð an enthusiast, if you are working diligently to acquire the taste, if you have simply enjoyed what you have tried so far and are looking to try something new, this may be the group for you. LetÕs get together once a month to share our favorites at someoneÕs home, to head out to one of San FranciscoÕs well stocked watering holes, or to descend en masse on one of the larger tasting events. An evening of Scotch and Whiskey drinking usually goes hand in hand with good conversation in relaxed company. I look forward to a comfortable and vibrant group.','food','Split','#Whiskey');
