insert into events values(2134717,10015,'2016/04/16','1399 Fremont St','Santa Clara','CA','95050','images/content/outdoor3.png','Play basketball','lots of pure, unadulterated fun! Now let''s go run','Meet other local Basketball fans and players. Whether youre a fan of Professional Teams, College Teams, Recreational Teams or just love a pick up game, join a Meetup Group near you and discuss the sport, leagues, etc. Play the game!How about we just run ? If you take joy in running any distance, then this might be a good group for you. We meetup at least once a week to run various distances. We are a diverse group of runners of different fitness levels. If youve never run before, youre also welcome to join one of our weekly runs to experience what youve been missing out on lots of pure, unadulterated fun! Now lets go run','outdoor','Split','#basketball');
